c: 23
v: 14
t: "dontho la umunali tidalipanga kukhala dontho la magazi ndipo dontho lamagazili tidalipanga kukhala m’bulu wa mnofu. Ndipo mnofu umenewu tidaukonza kukhala mafupa ndipo tidakuta mafupa ndi mnofu. Kotero tidamupanga iye kukhala chilengedwe china. odalitsa akhale Mulungu, Namalenga wabwino kwambiri mwa onse"